The providers of generative AI services (hereinafter “providers”) shall carry out pre-training, optimization training, and other activities handling training data in accordance with law, and comply with the following provisions:

(1) Use data and foundational models that have lawful sources;

(2) Where intellectual property rights are involved, the intellectual property rights that are lawfully enjoyed by others must not be infringed;

